Class RegionBuilder<R extends javafx.scene.layout.Region, B extends RegionBuilder<R,B>>

java.lang.Object
com.dua3.utility.fx.controls.abstract_builders.NodeBuilder<R,B>
com.dua3.utility.fx.controls.abstract_builders.RegionBuilder<R,B>
Type Parameters:
R - the type of Region to be built
B - the type of the concrete builder
Direct Known Subclasses:
ControlBuilder
public abstract class RegionBuilder<R extends javafx.scene.layout.Region, B extends RegionBuilder<R,B>> extends NodeBuilder<R,B>
An abstract base class for building Regions, providing a fluent API for configuring and creating instances of the Region type specified by the generic parameter R.
